Create a form that is NOT linked to a model with the following fields:

first_name: text

last_name: text

email :text

field set with the legend "Ice cream" for the following

favorite_icecream_flavor: select box with varieties of "chocolate", "butter pecan", "rocky road", "pistachio", "chunky fudge"

preference: radio button with cone or cup

likes: checkboxes with "sherbet", "sugar-free", "premium", "artisanal"


Don't forget to use labels -- the Rails way!



